cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a recommender system that retrieves similar stories based on shared literary themes.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of topic models to identify themes in episode transcripts.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are possible categories as the paper discusses the use of similarity measures and filtering options in the recommender system.
- cs.DL (Deep Learning) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on the use of deep learning techniques.
